hadiths[67]{hadithnumber,text}:
2308,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey logon key darmiyan faisla karney wala (jaj) muqarrar kiya gaya, usey (goya) baghair chhuri key zibeh kar diya gaya."
2309,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney qazi ka mansab talab kiya, wo apni jaan key hawaley kar diya jata hai, aur jisey us (mansab ko qubul kerney) par majbur kiya gaya, eik farishta nazil ho kar uski rehnumai karta hai."
2310,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Yamen rawana farmaya to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey rawana farma rahey hain ke unkey faisley karun, halanke main jawan hun (tajarba kaar nahin), mujhey to malum nahin faisla kaisey kiya jata hai? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kiya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney merey seeney par haath maara aur farmaya : aey Allah ! iskey dil ko hidayat dey aur iski zaban ko (sahih baat par) qaaim farma. wo farmatey hain : iskey baad mujhey do shakhson key darmiyan faisla kartey waqt kabhi shak pesh nahin aaya."
2311,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi Qazi logon key darmiyan faisley karta hai, qiyamat key din wo us haal mein hazir hoga ke eik farishtey ney usey guddi sey pakad rakha hoga, phir aasman ki taraf sar uthaeyga , agar Allah ney farmaya : usey phenk dey to farishta usey (jahannam key) gadhey mein phenk dega (jis mein wo) chaalis saal tak (girta chala jaeyga)."
2312,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala Qazi key sath hota hai jab tak wo zulm (be insafi) na karey. jab wo zulm karta hai to Allah Taala usey uskey nafs key supurd kar deta hai."
2313,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : rishwat deney waley aur rishwat leney waley par Allah ki lanat hai."
2314,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke aap ney farmaya : jab faisla karney wala faisla karey aur ijtihaad (koshish) kar key sahih baat tak pahunch jaey to uskey liye do sawab hain. aur jab faisla karey lekin ijtihaad karney mein us sey ghalati ho jaey to uskey liye eik sawab hai. yehi riwayat eik dusri sanad sey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
2315,"Hazrat Abu-Hashim (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke agar Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Rahimahullah) ki wo hadees na hoti jo unhoney apney walid (Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat ki hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Qazi teen (tarah key) hain. do jahannam mein jaeyngey aur eik jannat mein. (eik) wo aadmi (hai) jisney haq malum kar liya , phir uskey mutabiq faisla diya to wo jannat mein jaeyga. (doosra) wo aadmi (hai) jisney (haq sey) la ilm hotey huye logon mein faisla kiya, wo jahannam mein jaeyga. (teesra) wo aadmi (hai) jisney faisla kartey huye zulm sey kaam liya, wo bhi jahannam mein jaeyga. (agar ye hadees na hoti) to hum kehtey ke Qazi jab ijtihaad sey kaam ley (apni puri koshish kerey) to wo jannati hai."
2316,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Nufai bin Haris bin Kalda Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Qazi do aadmiyon key darmiyan faisla na karey jabke wo ghussay mein ho. (ustaad) Hisham ney apni riwayat mein ye alfaz bayan farmaaey hain : faisla karney waley key liye munasib nahin ke wo do aadmiyon key darmiyan faisla karey jabke wo ghussey mein ho."
2317,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum merey paas apney jhagdon ley kar aatey ho. aur main eik insan hi hun. shayad koi shakhs apni daleel ko doosrey ki nisbat behtar tor par bayan kar sakta ho. aur main to jo kuchh tum (fareeqain aur gawahon) sey sunta hun usi key mutabiq faisla karta hun, lihaza jis ko main uskey bhai key haq mein sey koi chiz dey dun to wo usey na ley. main to usey aag ka eik tukda dey raha hun. qiyamat key din wo usey ley kar hazir hoga."
2318,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main to mehaz eik insan hun. shayad tum mein sey eik shakhs apni daleel ko doosrey ki nisbat behtar tor par bayan kar sakta ho, lihaza jis ko uskey bhai key haq mein sey eik tukda kaat kar dey dun to main usey (jahannam ki) aag ka eik tukda kaat kar dey raha hun."
2319,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Jundub bin Junaada Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs is chiz ka daawey karey jo uski nahin to wo hum mein sey nahin, usey apna thikaana jahannam mein bana lena chahiye."
2320,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kisi muqaddmey mein zulm mein (zalim ki) madad ki, wo hamesha Allah ki narazi ka mustahiq rehta hai yahan tak key (us gunah sey) baaz aa jaey."
2321,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar logon ko mehaz unkey dawey ki bina par chiz dey di jaey to log doosrey afrad key jaan aur maal par dawey kar den lekin qism khana uske zimme hai jis par ilzaam lagaaya gaya hai."
2322,"Hazrat Ash'as bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : zamin ka eik tukda meri aur Yahudi ki mushtarka milkiyat tha. usney mera hissa taslim karney sey inkar kar diya. mainey usey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : kya terey paas koi gawah hai? mainey kaha : nahin. Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney Yahudi sey kaha : qism kha. mainey kaha : wo to (jhooti) qism kha kar mera maal ley ley ga. to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : (إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَشْتَرُونَ بِعَهْدِ ٱللَّهِ وَأَيْمَـٰنِهِمْ ثَمَنًا قَلِيلًا),''be shak jo log Allah key ehad aur apni qasmon ko thodi qeemat par bech daltey hain unkey liye aakhirat mein koi hissa nahin, Allah Taala na to un sey baat cheet kerega, na un ki taraf qiyamat key din dekhega, na unhen pak kerega, aur unkey liye dardnak azab hai.''"
2323,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney koi qism khai jabke wo qism khatey huye gunah (jhoot) ka kaam kar raha hai aur is (jhooti qasam) key zariey sey kisi musalman key maal ka kuchh hissa hasil karta hai, jab Allah sey uski mulaqat hogi to Allah is par naraz hoga."
2324,Hazrat Abu-Umama Haarisi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : jo shakhs qism kha kar kisi musalman aadmi ka haq maarta hai to Allah Taala is par jannat haram aur jahannam wajib kar deta hai. haazirin mein sey eik sahab ney kaha : agar-che koi maamuli si chiz ho? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar-che peelu ki eik miswak ho.
2325,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney merey is member key paas gunah wali (jhooti) qism khai, usey chahiye ke apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley agar-che taza miswak key liye (qasam khai) ho."
2326,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is member key paas jo bhi banda ya bandi gunah wali (jhooti) qism khayega, chahey taza miswak key liye khaye, uskey liye jahannam wajib ho jaeygi."
2327,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik Yahudi aalim ko bulaya aur farmaya : main tujhey us zaat ki qism deta hun jisney Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) par Torat nazil farmaai."
2328,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney do yahudiyon sey farmaya : main tumhen us Allah ki qism deta hun jisney Hazrat Musa (Alaihissalam) par Torat nazil farmaai."
2329,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ney eik janwer key barey mein daawey kiya, aur unkey darmiyan (faisla karney wali) koi gawahi mojud na thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke qism khaney key liye qura andazi kar lein. (phir jis ka qura nikley wo qism kha ley)."
2330,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke do aadmiyon ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney muqadma pesh kiya, unkey darmiyan (jhagdey ki wajeh) eik janwer tha. un mein sey kisi key paas gawah na tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un dono ko wo janwer aadha aadha taqseem kar diya (ke wo janwer farokht kar key qeemat aapas mein taqseem kar lein)."
2331,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ki koi chiz gum ho jaey ya chori ho jaey, phir usey wo chiz us shakhs key haath mein miley jo usey farokht kar raha hai to wo (Malik) us chiz ka ziyada haq rakhta hai aur kharidar bechney waley sey apni qeemat wasul kar ley."
2332,Hazrat Haram bin Saad bin Mahisa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bara bin Aazib bin Haris (Raziallahu anhuma) ki eik oontni logon key khet char jaya karti thi. wo kuchh logon key baagh mein ja ghusi aur usey kharab kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein waqia arz kiya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla farmaya ke maal (baagh waghera) ki hifazat din key waqt (baagh key) malikon ki zimmey daari hai. aur raat ko janwer jo kuch kharab karen uski talaafi janweron key malikon key zimmey hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey ye riwayat Bara bin Aazib sey bayan farmaai ke aale Bara ki eik oontni ney kisi ki kheti waghera kharab kar di to aap ney mazkura hadees ki tarah hi faisla farmaya.
2333,"Hazrat Qais bin Wahab Rahimahullah qabila banu Sawaat key eik aadmi sey riwayat kartey hain, usney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey arz kiya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key akhlaq key barey mein bataaiye. unhoney farmaya : kya to Quran nahin padhta? (jis mein ye irshad hai : )  (وَإِنَّكَ لَعَلَىٰ خُلُقٍ عَظِيمٍ), ''aap yaqinan azeem akhlaq key hamil hain.'' (uskey baad Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney) farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney as-haab key sath tashrif farma they. mainey aap key liye khana tayyar kiya. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney bhi aap key liye khana tayyar kiya. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ney pehley tayyar kar liya. mainey khaadima sey kaha : ja kar unka piyala ulat do. Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) abhi piyala Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney rakhney ka irada hi kar rahi thin ke khaadima ney unhen ja liya aur piyala ulat diya. piyala (gir kar) toot gaya aur khana bikhar gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney piyaley key tukdey jama kiye aur is mein jo khana tha wo chamdey key dastar khuwan par jama kiya aur sab ney khaya, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera piyala Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) key yahan bhej diya, aur wo unhi ko dey diya. aur farmaya : apney bartan ki jagah ye bartan ley lo. aur is mein jo khana hai wo bhi kha lo. (Ummul-mominin ney) farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key chehre Mubarak par naraazgi key asaar nazar nahin aaye."
2334,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) key yahan tashrif farma they. eik aur Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney eik piyaley mein khana bheja. unhoney laney wali key haath par haath maara to piyala gir kar toot gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney piyaley key dono tukdey ley kar eik doosrey sey milaaey aur us (tootey huye piyaley) mein khana dalney lagey aur farmaya : tumhari maa ko ghairat aa gaee thi. khana kha lo. chunanche unhoney khana khaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis zauja mohtarma key yahan tashrif farma they, wo apna piyala laeen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney wo sahih Salim piyala khana laney wali ko dey diya aur tootaa huwa unkey ghar rehney diya jinhoney wo toda tha."
2335,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi sey uska hamsaaya (padosi) uski deewar mein lakdi gaadney ki ijazat talab karey to (usey chahiye ke) usey mana na karey. (Abdur-Rehman Aaraj (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : ) jab Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye hadees sunai to saamein (sunne waalon) ney sar jhuka liye, chunanche jab Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen (is haal mein) dekha to farmaya : kya wajeh hai ke main tumhen is hadees sey aeraz kartey (bachte hue) mehsoos karta hun? Allah ki qism ! main is (hadees) ko tumharey kandhon par maaroonga."
2336,"Hazrat Ikrima bin Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke qabila banu Mughira key do bhai they. un mein sey eik ney qism kha li ke wo apni deewar par (kisi ko) shehteer nahin rakhney dega warna ghulam azad karega. is par Hazrat ikrima bin Salma (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai ke qabila banu Mughira key do bhai they. un mein sey eik ney qism kha li ke wo apni deewar par (kisi ko) shehteer nahin rakhney dega warna ghulam azad kerega. is par Hazrat Majmaa bin Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur bahut sey doosrey Ansari as-haab aagey aur unhoney kaha : hum gawahi detey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apney hamsaaey ko apni deewar par shehteer rakhney sey mana na karey. us (qasam khaney waley) aadmi ney kaha : merey bhai ! aap key haq mein , merey khilaf faisla ho gaya hai (aur main isey qubul karta hun) lekin mainey qism kha li hai to aap meri deewar key sath eik sutoon bana lein aur is par apna shehteer rakh lein."
2337,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi shakhs apney hamsaaey ko apni deewar par lakdi rakhney sey mana na kerey."
2338,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : raasta saat haath rakha karo."
2339,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab raastey key barey main tumhara ikhtilaf ho jaey to usey saat haath rakh liya karo."
2340,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney faisla diya : na (pehley pehal) kisi ko nuqsan pahunchana aur takleef dena jayez hai, na badley key tor par nuqsan pahunchana aur takleef dena."
2341,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na (pehley pehal) kisi ko nuqsan pahunchana aur takleef dena jayez hai, na badley key tor par nuqsan pahunchana aur takleef dena."
2342,"Hazrat Abu-Sarma (Malik bin Qais Ansari)  (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo ( kisi ko) nuqsan pahunchaeyga, Allah uska nuqsan kar dega aur jo kisi ko mushkil mein daleyga, Allah is par sakhti karega."
2343,Namraan bin Jaariya apney walid (Hazrat Jaariya bin Zafar (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat kartey hain ke kuchh logon ney eik jhaunpdi key barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein daawa kiya. wo (jhaunpdi) dono fariqon key istimal mein thi. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka faisla karney key liye bheja. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney un logon key haq mein faisla diya jinki taraf sarkandey ka naram hissa tha. jab wo wapis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur aap ko (is faisley ki) khabar di to aap ney farmaya : tu ney durust (faisla) kiya aur achcha faisla kiya.
2344,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab eik chiz do aadmiyon key haath farokht kar di jaey to pehley key haath bechnaa hi moatabar hoga. Abul-Waleed ney kaha : is hadees sey (doosrey kharidar ki taraf sey) qabza dilwaney ki shart najaaiz sabit hoti hai."
2345,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi key chhe ghulam they. uska unkey ilawa aur koi maal nahin tha. usney wafat key waqt un sab ko azad kar diya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey (teen) hissey kiye , phir do ghulamon ko azad kar diya aur chaar ko ghulam rehney diya."
2346,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik saudey mein do aadmiyon ka jhagda ho gaya . un mein sey kisi key paas sabut nahin tha (gawahi waghera ya koi aur tareeqa) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke qura dal kar qism kha lein, chahey unhen (qasam khana) pasand ho ya na-pasand ho."
2347,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi safar mein tashrif ley jatey to apni azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) (Raziallahu anhu) mein qura daltey.
2348,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen mein they to un ki khidmat mein teen mard hazir kiye gaey jinhoney eik aurat sey eik hi tuhur (paaki) mein jima (sambhog) kiya tha. (ab us aurat key bachey key barey mein jhagda ho gaya tha) Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney do aadmiyon sey puchha : kya tum dono is (teesrey) shakhs key haq mein bachchey ka iqrar kartey ho? un dono ney kaha : nahin. phir do aadmiyon (doosrey aur teesrey) sey farmaya : kya tum taslim kartey ho ke bachcha us (pehley) ka hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. (isi tarah teesrey aur pehley ko mukhatib kar key poochha) Hazrat Ali jab bhi (koi sey) do sey sawal kartey : kya tum taslim kartey ho ke bacha us (teesrey sathi) ka hai? to dono kehtey : nahin, chunanche aap ney un (teeno) key darmiyan qura dala aur jis key naam ka qura nikla bacha usi ka qarar dey diya aur uskey zimmey do tihai diyat dal di. ye waqia Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein arz kiya gaya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khul kar hansey yahan tak key aap ki daadhein zahir ho gaeen."
2349,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas bahut khush khush tashrif laye aur aap farma rahey they : Aaisha ! tumhen nahin malum ke aaj Mujaz'ziz Mudlaji merey paas aaya to usney Usama aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) ko dekha ke wo chadar odhey (letey) huye they. unhoney apney sar chupa rakhey they aur unkey paon nazar aa rahey they to us (Mujaz'ziz) ney kaha : ye paon eik doosrey sey miltey hain."
2350,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Quraish eik kaahin aurat key paas gaey aur us sey kaha : hamein ye bata ke maqame Ibrahim par jis shakhs ka nishan hai, hum mein sey kis ka nishane qadam us sey ziyada milta hai? usney kaha : agar tum humwaar retili zamin par eik chadar khinch kar (usey bilkul humwaar kar do, phir) is (ret) par chalo to main tumharey sawal ka jawab dey dungi. unhoney chadar khinchi, phir log us (humwaar ret) par chaley. us aurat ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qadame Mubarak key nishan ko dekh kar kaha : ye sahab us (Ibrahim (Alaihissalam)) sey sab sey ziyada mushaabihat rakhtey hain. uskey baad taqriban bees saal ya (kam o besh) jitna Allah ney chaha, utna arsa guzraa, phir Allah Taala ney Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (nabuwat ata farma kar) mab-us farma (bhaij) diya."
2351,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik bachchey ko uskey walid aur walida key darmiyan intikhaab ka moqey diya aur farmaya : ladkey ! ye teri walida hai aur ye tera walid hai (tu jis key sath chahey chala ja).
2352,"Hazrat Abdul-Hameed bin Salma (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey aur wo unkey dada sey riwayat kartey hain ke unkey waliden ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein muqadma pesh kiya, un mein sey eik kafir tha aur eik musalman tha. Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney bachchey ko ikhtiyar diya to wo kafir ki taraf maael huwa to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Allah ! isey hidayat dey. to wo musalman ki taraf maael ho gaya, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us (musalman) key haq mein faisla dey diya."
2353,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna aap farma rahey they : musalmanon key darmiyan suleh durust hai siwaye us suleh key jo kisi halal ko haram karey ya haram ko halal karey."
2354,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik sahab they, un ki aql kamzor thi. aur wo kharid aur farokht kartey they (to dhoka kha jatey they) unkey ghar walon ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! un par pabandi laga dijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen talab farmaya aur kharid aur farokht sey mana kar diya unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main kharid aur farokht sey sabr nahin kar sakta to aap ney farmaya : jab to kharid aur farokht karey to keh diya kar : dhoka na karna."
2355,"Janab Muhammad bin Yahya bin Hibban (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : wo merey par-dada Hazrat Munqid bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) they. unkey sar mein shadeed zakham aaya tha (jo dimagh ki jhilli tak pahuncha) is sey un ki zaban mein bhi luknat paida ho gaee thi, uskey bawajud wo tijarat tarak nahin kartey they aur un sey hamesha dhoka ho jata tha, chunanche unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar soorate haal arz ki to aap ney farmaya : jab tum lain-den karo to keh diya karo : dhoka nahin, phir tum jo chiz bhi kharido, us main tumhen teen din tak (wapis karney ka) ikhtiyar hoga, agar pasand aaye to rakh lo, napasand ho to uskey Malik ko wapis kar do."
2356,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik shakhs ney (baagh key) phal khareedey jin mein usey bahut khasara huwa aur wo bahut maqrooz ho gaya, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usey sadqa do. logon ney isey sadqa diya lekin us sey uska pura qarz ada nahin ho sakta tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qarz khuwahon sey farmaya : tumhen jo kuch milta hai ley lo, iskey siwa tumhen kuchh nahin milega."
2357,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko qarz khuwahon (chaahnewalon) key haath sey chhudaayaa, phir unhen Yamen mein aamil (governer ya zakat wasul karney ka zimmey-daar) muqarrar farma diya. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mera maal dey kar mujhey chhudaayaa, phir mujhey aamil bana diya."
2358,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey diwaliya qarar diye gaey shakhs key paas apni chiz joon ki toon mil gaee to ye shakhs dusron ki nisbat (muqabil) is chiz ka ziyada haq rakhta hai."
2359,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ney apni koi chiz bechi, wo chiz usey diwaliya qarar diye huye shakhs key paas waisi hi mil gaee jabke usney abhi uski qeemat mein sey kuchh bhi wasul nahin kiya tha to wo us (bechney waley) ki hai. aur agar usney qeemat ka kuchh hissa wasul kar liya ho to wo bhi doosrey qarz khuwahon key hukm mein hai."
2360,"Hazrat umr bin Khulda Zarqi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, aur wo Madina Munawra mein Qazi (jaj) they. unhoney farmaya : hamara eik sathi diwaliya ho gaya. hum uskey mamley mein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to unhoney farmaya : aisey hi shakhs key barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye faisla farmaya hai : jo shakhs faut ho jaey ya diwaliya ho jaey to saman ka Malik apney saman ka ziyada mustahiq hai, jab wo usey uskey paas waisa hi mil jaey."
2361,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur uskey paas kisi (qarz chahney wale) ka maal waisa hi mojud ho to qarz chahney wale ney us sey kuchh wasul kiya ho ya na kiya ho, (har haal mein) wo doosrey qarz khuwahon (chahney walon) ki tarah hi hai."
2362,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya gaya : kon log behtar hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey zamaney key (momin) afrad, phir jo un sey muttasil (lage hue) hongey, phir jo un sey muttasil hongey , phir aisey log aa jaeyngey jinki gawahi un ki qism sey pehley aur un ki qism un ki gawahi sey pehley aayegi."
2363,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney maqame jaabiya mein hum sey khitab farmaya : aap ney is mein farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey andar isi tarah khadey huye they jis tarah main tumharey andar khada hun, phir farmaya : merey Sahaba key barey mein mera khayal rakhna , phir un logon key barey mein jo un (Sahaba) sey muttasil (lage huey) hongey (yani Tabe-een), phir un logon key barey mein jo un (Tabe-een) sey muttasil hongey (yani Tabbe-Tabe-een), uskey baad jhoot aam ho jaeyga yahan tak key aadmi gawahi dega , halanke us sey gawahi talab nahin ki jaaeygi. aur wo qism khayega, halanke us sey qism nahin li jaeygi."
2364,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshade Mubarak suna : behtareen gawah wo hai jo gawahi ka mutalba kiye janey sey pehley hi gawahi dey dey."
2365,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney ye aayat padhi : (يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِذَا تَدَايَنتُم بِدَيْنٍ إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلٍ مُّسَمًّى)'''aey momino ! jab tum eik muqarrara muddat tak qarz lo ya do.'' yahan tak key aap is aayat par pahunchey : (فَإِنْ أَمِنَ بَعْضُكُم بَعْضً),''agar tum aapas main eik doosrey sey mutmain ho (to jisey amanat di gaee hai wo isey ada kerey).''  to farmaya : usney pehli aayat ko mansookh kar diya."
2366,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Hazrat Shuaib bin Muhammad) sey aur wo apney dada (Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhuma)) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khayanat karney waley mard aur aurat ki gawahi qubul nahin, aur na uski jisey Islam (laney key baad kisi jurm ki saza) mein had lagai gaee ho, aur na apney bhai sey adawat rakhney waley ki gawahi qubul hai."
2367,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : basti waley key khilaf khana-badosh ki gawahi qubul nahin."
2368,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (muddai ki) qism aur eik gawah key sath faisla farmaya.
2369,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (muddai ki) qism aur eik gawah key sath faisla farmaya.
2370,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik gawah aur (muddai ki) qism key sath faisla farmaya.
2371,Hazrat Sur'raq (bin Asad Juhni (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ki gawahi aur muddai ki qism ko durust qarar diya.
2372,"Hazrat Khuraim  (bin Akhram bin Shaddad bin Amr) bin Faatik Asadi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney subah ki namaz padhaai, phir jab aap ney salam pheraa to khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : jhooti gawahi ko shirk key barabar qarar diya gaya hai.  aap ney teen baar ye baat irshad farmaai, phir ye aayat padhi : (وَٱجْتَنِبُوا۟ قَوْلَ ٱلزُّورِ حُنَفَآءَ لِلَّهِ غَيْرَ مُشْرِكِينَ بِهِ),''aur jhooti baat sey perhez karo. Allah ki tohid ko mantey huye, uskey sath kisi ko shareek na kartey huye.''"
2373,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jhooti gawahi deney waley key qadam (hisab kitab key moqey par) apni jagah sey harkat nahin karengey yahan tak key Allah Taala uskey liye jahannam wajib kar dega."
2374,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ehale kitab ki eik doosrey key barey mein gawahi ko moatabar qarar diya.
